Filthy whore!

26
00:08:20.652 --> 00:08:22.234
ID confirmed.

27
00:08:26.277 --> 00:08:27.734
Go for exfiltration. Over.

28
00:08:53.191 --> 00:08:54.691
Clean the zone.

29
